fan_favorites.title: Fan Favorites
fan_favorites.description: From comics to wrestling, here's where you can dive into the beloved characters and epic stories that fanboys and fangirls love.

9386.title: Plan 9 from Outer Space
9386.description: Extraterrestrials invade the San Fernando Valley to stop humans from creating a doomsday device by reanimating the dead and causing total chaos.

136725.title: Thankskilling
136725.description: A murderous turkey hunts down five college kids on their Thanksiging break. Can the survivors break the curse and defeat the possessed bird?

255770.title: Power Morphicon Live
255770.description: Live interviews with cast and crew, bonus features, a special trivia contest, and much more at Power Morphicon 4!

264337.title: Stella: Live in Boston
264337.description: STELLA is the unique comedy trio known for their critically acclaimed Comedy Central series, their long-running nightclub show and their wildly popular series of shorts on the Web. Now STELLA (Michael Ian Black, Michael Showalter and David Wain) are captured live in concert in all of their uncensored glory.

283884.title: Dante's Inferno
283884.description: When his father and fiancee are murdered, a warrior must travel through the many circles of Hell in order to retrieve his true love from Lucifer.

284003.title: Street Fighter Alpha
284003.description: Brought together by the mysterious death of their martial arts master, Ken and Ryu must overcome a momentous challenge unlike any other.

286603.title: Asian Martial Arts Masters
286603.description: Explore the intense training and ability of the world's fiercest fighters, traditional weapons makers and experience the true spirit of Filipino fighting systems.

289793.title: Dead Space: Downfall
289793.description: A group of deep space miners discover an ancient artifact while on a mission to a faraway planet, accidentally releasing an unusual alien race.

289794.title: Dead Space: Aftermath
289794.description: Dead Space: Aftermath is a fast paced, horrifying thrill ride set in 2059 that follows the four surviving ship crew members aboard the USG O'Bannon.

289816.title: Ghost In The Shell
289816.description: See the groundbreaking original before the release of the live-action remake starring Scarlett Johansson! It is 2029 and a female cyborg hunts a hacker who robs humans of their memories.

294337.title: Lady Vengeance
294337.description: After serving 13 years in prison for her wrongful conviction of murdering a young boy, a woman’s first task is to track down the boy’s real killer.

300161.title: Cube 2: Hypercube
300161.description: Finding themselves trapped in cube-shaped rooms where the laws of physics are suspended, eight strangers must unlock the cubes' secrets to stay alive.

300162.title: Cube Zero
300162.description: When a group of eight strangers awaken in a trap-filled maze, one young man endeavors to save an innocent woman trapped inside.

300839.title: Mystery Team
300839.description: A group of young detectives are challenged to crack a murder case and finally prove themselves as real detectives once and for all, in this comedy.

300842.title: P2
300842.description: After leaving her office christmas party, a woman must survive the night when she is trapped in a parking garage with a deranged security guard.

301337.title: Hirokin: The Last Samurai
301337.description: In a post-apocalyptic and barren wasteland, a samurai with a troubled past sets off on a crucial mission, where he must make a difficult choice.

301339.title: Ju-On: The Grudge 2
301339.description: When a social worker enters a home where a family was once brutally killed, an evil spirit is awakened and triggers a terrifying chain of events.

302258.title: Tank Girl
302258.description: A mega-villain controls the world's water supply, and it's up to Tank Girl and her cohorts to end his reign.

302691.title: Killer Klowns From Outer Space
302691.description: Send in the clowns, this cult classic is back! One-of-a-kind alien invasion sci-fi featuring blood drinking alien clowns harvesting a small city.

305792.title: The Adventures Of Buckaroo Banzai
305792.description: A rock-star/brain-surgeon/comic-book-hero/samurai must stop evil creatures from the 8th dimension who want to conquer our dimension.

309700.title: Creature
309700.description: Scientists reach a remote planet only to find their rivals got there first, and are dead. Now, the creature that killed them hunts the new arrivals.

310493.title: Air Guitar Nation
310493.description: The guitars may be fake, but the competition is real as legions of aspiring mock stars head to the U.S. Air Guitar Championships in this colorful doc.

310501.title: Superheroes
310501.description: What if superheroes were real? Meet the real-life, self-proclaimed crime fighters who don masks and capes and attempt to bring justice to evildoers.

312629.title: Dragon Age Redemption
312629.description: An Elven assassin journeys to eliminate a Qunari mage with aspirations of anarchy in this fantasy series inspired by the BioWare video game.

312634.title: A Simple Walk Into Mordor
312634.description: Two superfans attempt to walk over 120 miles across New Zealand from the filming location of Hobbiton to the real life Mount Doom in just six days.

314039.title: Sharknado: Feeding Frenzy
314039.description: What began as another Syfy Channel creature feature has now become an important piece of pop culture  poised to take over the entire world.

314041.title: 13 Nights of Elvira: Night of the Living Dead
314041.description: Elvira resurrects the original zombie classic, and devours it with raw energy!  Elvira loves George A Romero's masterpiece so much, she's takin it to the grave!

314506.title: Heavenly Sword
314506.description: When tasked with bringing a magical sword to its rightful owner, a female warrior uses the sword to stop a vicious king from obtaining it for evil.

314897.title: State of Play
314897.description: Every year thousands of South-Koreans flock to the game stadiums in Seoul to watch the Pro League, a live sports event where professional gamers compete to be the best at one single video game: Starcraft.

316277.title: GLOW: The Story of the Gorgeous Ladies of Wrestling
316277.description: This heartfelt documentary chronicles the rise and fall of the first-ever all-female pro-wrestling show through the stories of those who lived it.

316420.title: Bloodrayne
316420.description: After escaping a travelling circus, an 18th century vampire joins a group of vampire hunters to avenge her mother's rape — and kill her father.

316421.title: Bloodrayne 2: Deliverance
316421.description: In the nineteenth century, a half-vampire human must fight off Billy the Kid and his vampire gang when she arrives in the Wild West.

316459.title: Cube
316459.description: Seven strangers find themselves imprisoned in a seemingly endless maze filled with deadly traps and must fight to escape,  despite the odds.

318227.title: Cheech & Chong: Puff Puff Laugh
318227.description: Cheech & Chong host a hazy night full of stoner comedy at Just for Laughs in Montreal, the largest international comedy festival in the world.

321860.title: Fred 2: Night of the Living Fred
321860.description: After Fred's music teacher is replaced, he grows to suspect that the new teacher is a vampire, sending him on a mission with his friends to prove it.

329511.title: Fanquest: Twilight
329511.description: Melissa Rycroft (“The Bachelor”) takes fans of the “Twilight” series to the movie franchise’s secret locations in Vancouver, Canada and Paraty, Brazil. Experience the series like never before!

332933.title: Fred 3: Camp Fred
332933.description: After ending up at the wrong summer camp, Fred makes the best of a bad situation and vows to help his fellow campers win the annual games.

332938.title: Repo: The Genetic Opera
332938.description: In 2056, an epidemic of organ failures devastates the planet and those who cannot afford their treatments are hunted by villainous Repo Men.

367719.title: Mega Shark vs Crocosaurus
367719.description: The massive prehistoric shark has survived and the world is again threatened when a new, more dangerous foe is discovered in the jungles of Africa.

367720.title: Mega Shark vs Giant Octopus
367720.description: Two prehistoric sea creatures, a mega shark and a giant octopus, fight to the death on the California coast. Who will reign supreme over the sea?

367721.title: Mega Shark VS Kolossus
367721.description: The world must figure out how to stop a mega shark and a Cold War-era giant robot doomsday device before they destroy everything on land and sea.

367722.title: Mega Shark vs Mecha Shark
367722.description: When a new Mega Shark menaces mankind, the government unleashes the Mecha Shark to defeat the monster in a pitched battle that threatens the planet.

372424.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Bonds Beyond Time
372424.description: For the first time, Yugi, Jaden and Yusei fight together against when a time traveler comes to destroy the Duel Monsters game!

385365.title: A Gamer's Life
385365.description: In this documentary about an unconventional career, two professional gamers share tips and tricks on how they earn money from playing video games.

399751.title: Heroes Manufactured
399751.description: Comic book artists reveal their secrets and abilities with breaking into the comic book industry while dealing with fandom, celebrities and the craze of comic book conventions.

404623.title: Battle Royale
404623.description: A group of students from a Japanese high school are forced to compete in a battle, killing one another until only one is left standing.

409840.title: Reaper
409840.description: A supernatural  killer descends on an mysterious town and a group of drifters and criminals band together to defeat it before it all goes to hell.

409844.title: Spaghettiman
409844.description: After an incident with a bowl of spaghetti and a malfunctioning microwave, Clark becomes a superhero that fights crime with spaghetti...for a cost.

414733.title: 24 Hour Comic
414733.description: In Portland Oregon, eight artists come together to participate in Scott McCloud's 24 Hour Comic Challenge, attempting to write, draw, and complete a 24 page comic, in 24 hours.

415644.title: The Dinosaur Project
415644.description: When their helicopter is brought down by a flock of huge birds, a team of explorers discover strange creatures thought extinct for millions of years.

415646.title: Doomed! the Untold Story of Roger Corman's Fantastic Four
415646.description: A documentary that tells the history of the ill-fated movie version of the Fantastic Four that was executive produced by Roger Corman.

417712.title: Mother's Day
417712.description: When her sons break into a home and take the owners and their guests hostage, a mother teaches them all what real torture is all about.

417720.title: Tekken
417720.description: In 2039, when territories are run by corporations, a warrior rises from the streets to avenge his mother's death by entering a fighting competition.

417722.title: Battle Royale II - Requiem
417722.description: Three years after the events in BATTLE ROYALE, Shuya Nanahara is a  well-known terrorist bent on bringing down the government. In response, they order the creation of the "Battle Royale 2" program, sending a class of junior-high students to catch and kill him.

432267.title: Night of the Comet
432267.description: When a passing comet snuffs out most of humanity, a pair of very ’80s Valley Girls hit the mall and battle hordes of blood-thirsty zombies.

436722.title: Birth of the Living Dead
436722.description: The story of a college drop-out who went to Pittsburgh, gathered real townspeople to help make ‘Night of the Living Dead,’ and put zombies on the map.

441460.title: The Hungover Games
441460.description: Three friends wake up from a night of revelry in a futuristic dystopia and battle their way through the pop culture districts of The Hungover Games.

449441.title: Art of the Game: Ukiyo-E Heroes
449441.description: Two artists – one American and one Canadian – team up despite their generation gap to make woodcut art based on two iconic video game characters.

449562.title: Mazes and Monsters
449562.description: When a college student and his pals play their favorite board game in a fabled local cavern, fantasy and reality merge into a harrowing escapade.

455326.title: Electra Woman & Dyna Girl
455326.description: A crime-fighting duo ups the stakes with their crime fighting skills and personas when they move from small town Ohio to glamorous Los Angeles.

455955.title: Minecraft: The Story of Minecraft
455955.description: People don't just play Minecraft, they get lost in a digital universe. This documentary explores the game's unrivaled impact across the globe.

455984.title: Minecraft: Into the Nether
455984.description: Explore the phenomenon of Minecraft, the video game whose vast digital world and fervid fans have given rise to a new breed of YouTube celebrity.

456106.title: Dead Rising: Watchtower
456106.description: A zombie virus outbreak throws a city into chaos as a trio of survivors must develop an arsenal of makeshift weapons to battle the apocalypse.

456639.title: Cosplay Culture
456639.description: Darth Vader, Lara Croft and Bilbo Baggins share a latte. Captain America, Superwoman and Naruto wait in line for the toilet. Welcome to the world of cosplay.

464312.title: Star Wars vs. Star Trek
464312.description: Battling it out for pop-culture dominance since 1977, Star Wars and Star Trek have changing the face of science-fiction, and fandom, forever.

465146.title: Red Sonja: Queen of Plagues
465146.description: A redheaded warrior faces impossible odds as she leads a doomed army against a fearsome opponent from her past in this animated comic.

465938.title: Mythica: The Iron Crown
465938.description: Unlikely heroes hijack a battle wagon as a wizard steals an artifact that, in the wrong hands, will flood the land with legions of the evil undead.

465939.title: Mythica: The Godslayer
465939.description: A cursed sorceress leads a quest for a weapon of the gods, but when her sworn enemy joins her she must find good within or the world will be enslaved.

466653.title: Solarbabies
466653.description: Imprisoned orphans in a drought-plagued future cross a parched wasteland in search of an all-powerful orb that could bring water to their world.

469522.title: Dead Space
469522.description: Intergalactic horror with desperate hope for a cure awaits the crew of a Saturn space station as a deadly virus begins to attack them one by one.

469752.title: Game Changers
469752.description: Two former eSports legends toiling at a failing IT company hatch a plan to reenter the gaming circuit and reclaim their status as pro gamers.

470313.title: Bloodrayne 3
470313.description: While battling Nazis during World War II, Rayne must stop a demented scientist from using her vampire blood to make Hitler immortal.

472705.title: Double Dragon
472705.description: Based on the video game, two teenage brothers use their fighting prowess to take on a rich mega-villain who's after their magical medallion.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

475895.title: Creepshow 2
475895.description: Three gruesome tales of brutality, vengeance and the uncanny are unveiled in this this anthology horror movie based on the stories of Stephen King.

478163.title: Arcade
478163.description: All the kids in town are dying to play an addictive new video game. A teen discovers that the game has a mysterious and dangerous twist.

478798.title: Hellraiser
478798.description: This cult classic tells the story of an unfaithful wife and her dead lover. The chilling nightmare introduces the iconic demon Pinhead.

478812.title: Hellbound: Hellraiser II
478812.description: This brutal sequel follows Kristy, as she is brought to an institution. The facilities won't keep her safe from the return of a certain demon.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

491026.title: Fortnite: Battle, Build, Survive!
491026.description: Grab your pickaxe, jump out of the battle bus and join us on the battlefield as we explore one of the biggest games the world has ever seen.

492575.title: Overwatch: Be the Hero
492575.description: As one of the fastest growing games of all time, Overwatch has become a global phenomenon. Why is this game so universally appealing?

499391.title: Chris Claremont's X-Men
499391.description: Assigned to a comic on the brink of cancellation, writer Chris Claremont spent years revitalizing the X-Men franchise into a cultural juggernaut.

499787.title: Geek and You Shall Find
499787.description: Three filmmakers delve into the layered and complex superhero culture by exploring the creation of some of its most famous comics and characters.

504436.title: A Brony Tale
504436.description: The unexpected rise to internet stardom of a Canadian voice over artist when she was cast as Apple Jack and Rainbow Dash in a My Little Pony remake.

505480.title: The Faces of Fortnite
505480.description: Meet the Twitch streamers and online entertainers and who helped make the multiplayer game Fortnite the global juggernaut it is today.

505500.title: Minecraft: Through the Nether Portal
505500.description: Learn how the sandbox game Minecraft is being used as an educational tool, featuring interviews with industry experts and YouTube’s biggest gamers.

505738.title: A Minecraft Ninja Turtle Movie
505738.description: A group of first-person video game characters team with the Ninja Turtles in a series of digital mines to battle evil forces threatening their world.

505740.title: Little Lizard - The Unofficial Fortnite Skit
505740.description: CGI-animated adventure of first-person action as an armed squad of heroes chases the villain Rapscallion across many game-console dimensions.

513071.title: What We Left Behind: Looking Back at Star Trek: Deep Space Nine
513071.description: The legacy of Star Trek: Deep Space Nine is explored through new interviews with cast and crew members.

513375.title: Uncle Art
513375.description: A portrait of the pioneer behind iconic gaming music of the 80s and 90s follows him, as he re-invents tunes at Abbey Road with a 50-piece orchestra.

513780.title: American Jedi
513780.description: Follow Star Wars fans who’ve abandoned their personal religions for Jedi-ism and must reconcile their dark issues in order to attain Knighthood.

513843.title: League of Legends: Learning to Lead
513843.description: A look at the culture surrounding the competitive game and e-sport, which draws everyone from students to salaried, professional gamers.

516056.title: Zero Charisma
516056.description: The passionate game master of a fantasy role-play tournament goes haywire, when a magnetic hipster joins his group and threatens to steal his power.

517863.title: The Fantasy Makers: Tolkien, Lewis, and MacDonald
517863.description: Imaginative documentary about fantasy writers and legends J.R.R. Tolkien, C.S. Lewis, and George MacDonald’s vivid legacy in pop-culture today.

518502.title: Madness in the Method
518502.description: As an actor with few chances to branch out, Jason Mewes vows to take his career more seriously, but he winds up connected to a series of crimes.

520883.title: Eye of the Beholder: The Art of Dungeons & Dragons
520883.description: Designers, authors, fans and corporate insiders of Dungeons & Dragons share fascinating facts in this documentary about the iconic role-playing-game.

522000.title: United We Fan
522000.description: For superfans, TV shows represent a community that’s worth defending. Stars, creators, and enthusiasts discuss what their shows mean to them.

522072.title: Silent Hill
522072.description: A mother desperately searches for her adopted daughter through a town that’s been possessed by an evil force. Can she find her in time?

527969.title: Ghostheads
527969.description: Strap on your proton pack and enter the world of extreme Ghostbusters fandom featuring cast and crew interviews and stories from fans themselves.

528435.title: The Fellows Hip - Rise of the Gamers
528435.description: A loveable loser and his three equally geeky buddies get their first taste of belonging when a Lord of the Rings gaming competition comes to town.

530179.title: Danger God
530179.description: Meet Gary Kent, a stuntman who dominated action-packed B-movies in the ‘60s and ‘70s, who took on practical action sequences one challenge at a time.

530301.title: Lost Heroes
530301.description: A documentary spotlighting Canada's forgotten comic book superheroes and their legendary creators

533872.title: Get Thrashed: The Story of Thrash Metal
533872.description: An intimate look at the biggest bands in the heavy metal music scene, as they reveal show footage, discuss drugs, crazy hair, and their journey.

537473.title: Lost Soul: The Doomed Journey of Richard Stanley's Island of Dr. Moreau
537473.description: A look behind the scenes of the 1996 critical failure. Hollywood’s biggest stars and producers bet on this movie, so what went wrong?

538805.title: Master of Dark Shadows
538805.description: A behind-the-scenes look at the fascinating impact of filmmaker Dan Curtis, the creative mind behind the groundbreaking gothic drama Dark Shadows.

540241.title: Street Fighter: The New Challengers
540241.description: Comic book hero Ryu travels the world, Cammy searches for her past, Chun-Li investigates the Hong Kong underworld, and Ken faces a vengeful Vega.

541570.title: Little Lizard Gaming: Minecraft Day of the Dragons
541570.description: Learn how to train your Minecraft dragon with Little Lizard, Tiny Turtle and Scuba Steve!

543067.title: Street Fighter: Round One: Fight!
543067.description: Based on the popular video game, this story follows Ken and Ryu, who are tracked by  the host of a fighter tournament, as they solve a mystery.

546215.title: VHS Revolution
546215.description: The history of the VHS cassette, from its global journey as a game changer in 1980s home entertainment to modern-day tributes for the iconic VCR tape.

552653.title: VHS Nasty
552653.description: An in-depth look at censorship within horror films that shook not only Britain in the early 1980s, but the world, into a frenzy of panic.

553390.title: Zombies
553390.description: Learn the legends and facts behind these ever-popular flesh-eating monsters rising from their graves and ambling around after our yummy brain food.

553394.title: Darla's Book Club: Discussing the Game of Thrones
553394.description: The literary fantasy world of magic, battles, dragons, and scandalous intrigue in the “Game of Thrones” book series is explored here in a novel way.

553398.title: Darla's Book Club: Discussing the Harry Potter Series
553398.description: A must-watch for Potterheads and those new to the series, get the inside scoop on all things Harry and Hogwarts with trusty book club leader, Darla.

553972.title: Greetings From Tromaville!
553972.description: Follow the 40-plus year run of cult comedic horror films that came out of the world's longest running independent film studio, Troma Entertainment.

557807.title: The Fate of the Swordsman
557807.description: An adrenaline-filled action spectacular about a martial artist master in over his head when he’s surrounded by deadly masters with dark motives.

559826.title: Texas Chain Saw Massacre: The Shocking Truth
559826.description: How did the cult classic about a cannibalistic family of psychopaths ever get made? This doc speaks to the original cast and crew to get the scoop.

560778.title: The Captains
560778.description: Follow Kirk into the final frontier as he interviews the elite group of actors who have played fellow Starship captains in the Star Trek franchise.

560790.title: Chaos on the Bridge
560790.description: The original captain of the USS Enterprise goes behind the camera to interview the production team responsible for Star Trek: The Next Generation.

560807.title: Get a Life!
560807.description: William Shatner examines the cultural phenomena of Star Trek, its fan-following and his own role within it, in a documentary based on his book.

561901.title: Zebraman (Subbed)
561901.description: A depressed man's alter ego becomes his saving grace after he uses his fantasy persona to battle criminals and an intergalactic conspiracy.

562030.title: Kirby at War
562030.description: The beloved comic book artist behind The Avengers, Black Panther, Hulk, and The X-Men was a World War II veteran, which shaped his artistic lens.

562035.title: The Universe of Keith Haring
562035.description: A portrait of the stellar life and works of the NY pop artist features film and audio clips of Haring and interviews with an array of cultural icons.

563160.title: Max Payne
563160.description: A cop hellbent on revenge tracks down those responsible for the brutal murder of his family, but his obsession takes him on a nightmarish journey.

564328.title: Lovecraft: Fear of the Unknown
564328.description: Fantasy, horror, and science fiction authors and filmmakers dissect the life, work, and legacy of the brainchild of the Cthulhu Mythos universe.

565171.title: King Cohen
565171.description: A look back at the popular B-movie era, this documentary celebrates the career of iconic horror and exploitation movie writer-producer Larry Cohen.

565722.title: Nintendo Quest: The Most Unofficial and Unauthorized Nintendo Documentary Ever!
565722.description: Without the use of online ordering, a passionate video game fan has 30 days to collect every title ever released for the Nintendo console.

565749.title: To Hell and Back: The Kane Hodder Story
565749.description: Known for his work as Jason in Friday the 13th, stuntman Hodder’s life has encompassed a traumatic childhood and a near-death accident.

566301.title: Kim Dotcom
566301.description: The incredible true story of Kim Dotcom, founder of file hosting site Megaupload, as he fights extradition to the United States on a host of charges.

571720.title: Sopranos Behind the Scenes (Vol. 2 of 2)
571720.description: The making of Season 6 of “The Sopranos” series is here, along with bloopers and cast interviews, in this independent special that will thrill fans.

571816.title: Action Heroes of Movies & TV - Captain Marvel, Superman, Batman, Lone Ranger & More
571816.description: From Batman and Robin to Flash Gordon and Tarzan, see the knuckle-busting film and television action characters that gave birth to the genre.

571817.title: Horrible Horror
571817.description: This one’s for you, low-budget horror fans: Enjoy bite-sized versions of “Screaming Skull,” “Santa Claus Conquers the Martians,” and many more.

575100.title: The Sci-Fi Boys
575100.description: “Lord of the Rings” maestro Peter Jackson hosts this cinematic look back at special effects pioneers and the directors they inspired with their work.

575434.title: 24x36: A Movie About Movie Posters
575434.description: Meet the artists who created beloved film poster illustrations, and learn Hollywood’s turbulent history with illustrated cinema art.

577086.title: DOA: Dead or Alive
577086.description: Four of the world’s best fighters are invited to a martial arts contest, where they learn the sinister real intentions of the tournament.

577995.title: Grant Morrison: Talking With Gods
577995.description: Grant Morrison is one of the most popular writers in comics, and one of the most controversial. He is the Rock Star of Comics, a philosopher and chaos magician, who has used his comics to change both himself and his audience.

581144.title: Films of Fury: The Kung Fu Movie Movie
581144.description: A history of martial arts films, from their roots to the 1970s heyday of action-packed fight fests and beyond, featuring the superstars of the genre.

588315.title: Kings of Cult
588315.description: Mavericks of strange cinema, Roger Corman and Charles Band, discuss their work, their fans, the careers they launched, and the future of the industry.

588414.title: Vampira and Me
588414.description: Trace the rise and fall of coat-check attendant-turned-actress Maila Nurmi who hit the late-night TV airwaves in 1954 as the glamour ghoul Vampira.

589448.title: Romantic Comedy
589448.description: A musician and writer is joined by movie critics, actors and filmmakers to unpack the history, present, and future of the romantic comedy genre.

592088.title: Gamera: Destroy All Planets
592088.description: When two children encounter a flying turtle, they free him from an extraterrestrial’s spell, which allows him to defend mankind from a monster.

594150.title: Time Warp: The Greatest Cult Films of All Time (Vol. 3): Comedy & Camp
594150.description: From Fast Times at Ridgemont High and Office Space to Monty Python and Showgirls, hear from the cast and crew who made these films cult classics.

594174.title: Time Warp: The Greatest Cult Films of All Time (Vol. 2): Horror & Sci-Fi
594174.description: From Night of the Living Dead and The Texas Chainsaw Massacre to A Clockwork Orange, hear from the cast and crew who made these films cult classics.

594423.title: Trailer War
594423.description: The Alamo Drafthouse has gathered the most fascinating, strangest, and entertaining coming attraction trailers mankind has ever known.

595394.title: Raiders! The Story of the Greatest Fan Film Ever Made
595394.description: After Steven Spielberg's classic Raiders of the Lost Ark was released 35 years ago, three 11-year-old boys set out on what would become a 7-year-long labor of love and tribute to their favorite film: a shot-for-shot remake of the film.

599129.title: Ghostbusters: Behind Closed Doors
599129.description: The director, producer, stars and crew share stories from the making of 'Ghostbusters.'

03497.title: Fanboy Confessional
03497.description: "Fanboy", "Geek" and "Nerd" were once terms of ridicule but today folks wear these badges proudly. There are now millions of self-professed Fanboys and Fangirls building active communities around the world. It's no longer just about collecting things - it's about collecting experiences. Fanboy Confessional gets inside these experiences and reveals heretofore-secret worlds, celebrating the real superheroes - the fans.

03427.title: Last Fan Standing
03427.description: The universe's most knowledgeable nerds get quizzed on sci-fi, horror and superheroes in this witty game show that puts fandom to the test.

02100.title: Sonic X
02100.description: A malfunction sends Sonic the Hedgehog to Earth where he meets Chris, who helps collect Chaos Emeralds so Sonic and friends can go home.

01100.title: Sonic Underground
01100.description: Sonic, Manic and Sonia must fight Dr. Robotnik and his two sidekicks, Sleet and Dingo and the SWAT Bots, with the aid of their metal medallions and bring peace to Mobius and find mother!

0300004785.title: Epic Fantasy Painting in Oils
0300004785.description: Learn techniques from an artist with over 20 years inside the video games industry’s top franchises from Magic the Gathering to World of Warcraft.

0942.title: Backlot
0942.description: Original series from Shout Factory TV, Backlot features interviews and behind the scenes looks at some of your favorite shows and films, plus exclusive special events.

02333.title: Comic Book Heroes
02333.description: Perth based friends Wolfgang Bylsma and Skye Walker Ogden are geeks on a winning streak. Comic Book Heroes tracks these two passionate small-town publishers, and their team of talented artists and writers, as they set out to conquer the ruthless, bizarre and potentially very lucrative world of the American comic book industry.

02067.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!
02067.description: Follows the adventures of teenager Yugi, whose magical secret comes to life when he plays his favorite card game: 'Duel Monsters.'

04510.title: Beauty and the Geek Australia
04510.description: Stunning girls and genius guys live together and team up as they compete in hilarious and heart-warming challenges to test their intellect and social skills.

03364.title: Legend of Zelda
03364.description: To stop an evil wizard from ruling the kingdom, Link and Princess Zelda must prevent a magical artifact from falling into his clutches.

0300005213.title: Superman: The Lost Episodes
0300005213.description: Produced after Max Fleischer's initial animated series, these eight episodes were produced by the newly formed Famous Studios in fully restored color.

02387.title: Earthsea
02387.description: A reckless youth is destined to become the greatest sorcerer that the mystical land of Earthsea has ever known.

03325.title: Highlander
03325.description: As one of the immortals, entities who have waged a war between good and evil for centuries, a 400-year-old Scotsman fights for his destiny.

0400.title: Wilfred
0400.description: Adam is the only one who sees Wilfred, his girlfriend’s dog, as a man in a dog suit, in the original version of the Australian series.

0300006271.title: Sneaky Stripes Minecraft Gameplay: Zebra Gamer
0300006271.description: The popular video game fan, known on YouTube as Zebra Gamer, takes viewers through 15 different levels of Minecraft Co-Op with his best friend.

03456.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL
03456.description: Aspiring duelist Yuma and strange visitor Astral team up so Yuma can learn the art of the duel while Astral gets the help he needs to regain his memories.

02362.title: Sam & Max
02362.description: Sam & Max are freelance police and view the world as their own personal theme park.

0300007024.title: Donkey Kong Country
0300007024.description: Inspired by the beloved video game, this CGI animated series follows Donkey Kong and pal Diddy Kong in their journey to defeat the evil King K. Rool.

0300005414.title: Ultraforce
0300005414.description: Superheroes are commissioned by the U.S. government to protect the world from their terrorist counterparts, who have evil plans to take over.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

01495.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's
01495.description: New Domino City, the playground to legendary duelist Yugi Muto, has been transformed into a futuristic society where dueling has kicked into overdrive.

03455.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX
03455.description: Follow a new generation of duelists at the prestigious Duel Academy—a highly competitive boarding school where pencils and books have been replaced by Duel Disks and monster cards!

0926.title: Dan Vs.
0926.description: Dan thinks the whole world is against him. Maybe it is, and maybe it isn't -- not even his laid-back friend Chris is totally sure. Maybe Dan's just imagining it all. But, like Chris, you can't help going along for the ride when Dan dreams up his wild plots to get even with whoever or whatever he thinks is out to get him.

0300006746.title: Bollywood: The World's Biggest Film Industry
0300006746.description: A show that steps exclusively behind the scenes of the world’s biggest film industry, Bollywood, with    access to its stars, stories, and secrets.

0833.title: Life's a Trip
0833.description: Experience the real, unedited, and sometimes crude side of the most fascinating diversions our planet has to offer worldwide

02383.title: Mutant X
02383.description: A genetic engineer goes on the run with his four created mutants while seeking their own kind while a shady government operative tracks them down.

03393.title: MXC: Most Extreme Elimination Challenge
03393.description: Two teams compete in some of the funniest and most hazardous games ever made for TV in this hilarious spoof of extreme sports competitions.

0300006332.title: Crazy Craft Minecraft Survival (Sigils)
0300006332.description: Join your favorite gamer friends as they take on the thrilling world of Crazy Craft, also known as the most unpredictable Minecraft Mod Pack.

0300005973.title: Inside Horror
0300005973.description: Horror movie fans are invited to join hosts Eiric and Staci, as they engage in conversations with some of the greatest minds behind the genre.

0300004799.title: Double Dragon
0300004799.description: Fraternal twin brothers destined to be great martial arts warriors fight evil in this animated series based on a video game.

04749.title: The Aquabats! Super Show!
04749.description: A rock band consisting of five superheroes battle monsters in a retro campy style, complete with fake commercials and the heroes in cartoon form.

0300004829.title: Tiny Plastic Men
0300004829.description: Low-level employees of the Gottfried Brothers toy company test products for defects in their basement office that looks more like a nerdy frat house.

04860.title: Heroes Manufactured: Creators Unleashed
04860.description: Explore North America's Comic Cons, which connect fans to pop culture talent. Learn about the world of illustration, cosplay, toy marketing, and more.

04550.title: Virtua Fighter
04550.description: Join Akira Yuki as he discovers his character so he can see the eight shining stars that are only visible to those who have mastered this strength.

03599.title: Dev Diary
03599.description: Video game developers race to bring their latest program to market while struggling with devastating personal challenges in this docuseries.

02066.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V
02066.description: Yuya Sakaki’s dream is and become the greatest “duel-tainer” in history, like his father, and he just might pull it off!

0300006356.title: Alien Autopsy
0300006356.description: Jonathan Frakes presents this bold documentary, which travels to Roswell, New Mexico in search of answers about legendary UFO sightings.

0300006352.title: The Captains Close Up
0300006352.description: William Shatner hosts this exciting series, which includes interviews with the many talented actors who portrayed Star Trek captains.

01619.title: Comedy Kings
01619.description: Comedy Kings delivers stand-up performances from some of the world’s best comics. Filmed at the prestigious Just For Laughs festival in Montreal. Featuring Aziz Ansari and Louis C.K.

0300005711.title: The Story of Film: An Odyssey
0300005711.description: The grand evolution of motion pictures is examined and critiqued through the use of film clips and interviews with legendary artists and scholars.

054.title: Spaced
054.description: Directionless Daisy Steiner and wired urban surfer Tim Bisley are twenty-somethings who lie about being a married in order to rent a London flat.

03253.title: Space 1999
03253.description: The crew of Moonbase Alpha must struggle to survive when the force from a massive explosion throws the moon out of orbit and into deep space.

01622.title: Naruto (Subtitled)
01622.description: 12 years ago, the Nine-Tailed Fox claimed many lives before its spirit was contained with a baby boy who has now grown to become a ninja-in-training.

0300006462.title: Camp Minecraft Survival (Sigils)
0300006462.description: Laugh along with popular gamer Sigils and his friends, as they tap into the Camp Minecraft Server for hilarious moments and epic fails.

0300005477.title: A Toy Store Near You
0300005477.description: Shot by the shop owners themselves, go inside over 40 vintage toy stores and hear how they are surviving and playing amid the COVID 19 Pandemic.

03704.title: Geeking Out
03704.description: Kevin Smith and Greg Grunberg host this pop-culture talk show that gives fans an all-access pass to their favorite shows, movies and comics.

03349.title: Super Mario World
03349.description: King Koopa is on the loose, and he's ready to battle the Super Mario Bros. using a powerful new weapon: his own children!
